Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要从Ahnenerbe出走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什么完全不明白喵
