Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被抓住就没事了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都说不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让远野同学太为难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  远野同学
